##Â Search Rescues [GET /api/search/rescues]

Search records of rescues by matching fields

Scope: public

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + active: `true` (boolean) - Return records that are currently active
      + codeRed: `true` (boolean) - Return records that are marked as code red

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + links (Link) - Links
      + meta (Meta) - Statistics on the current result
      + data (array[Rescue]) - A list of rescues
